# Directions to L100 Theology Trainer (Grisham, mob 336)

say { "hello";
	say Hello %n, what can I help you with?;
	}

say { "trainer";
	tell %n Yes I can help you there... ;
	tell %n but I can only give you a hint.....;
	tell %n Travel west of Grimhaven...;
	tell %n to where the Lan'Quin forest is.;
	tell %n I'd be careful in there.;
	tell %n Large bears will attack if you're not careful.;
	tell %n Best to travel in the company of others..;
	}

